      <h1 class='title'>Pigs</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 cc237-8WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_237ws' title='Col. 237WS &mdash; HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c237WS' name='column_237ws' href='#column_237ws' rel='bookmark'>237WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06078'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_133'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-alan-hurst' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_133' title='Link to this speech by Mr Alan Hurst' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-alan-hurst" title="Mr Alan Hurst">Mr. Hurst</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06078">To ask the Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs how many pigs were slaughtered in abattoirs in the United Kingdom in each year between 1990 to 2001. [87291]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06079'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_134'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-elliot-morley' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_134' title='Link to this speech by Mr Elliot Morley' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-elliot-morley" title="Mr Elliot Morley">Mr. Morley</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06079">The information requested is given in the table below:<table>
          <tr>
          <td><span class="italic">Number of pigs slaughtered in abattoirs in the United Kingdom 1990&#x2013;2001</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td><span class="italic">Unit: Thousand head</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td><span class="italic">Clean Pigs</span></td>
          <td><span class="italic">Sows and AdultBoars</span></td>
          <td><span class="italic">Total Pigs</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1990</td>
          <td>13,879</td>
          <td>325</td>
          <td>14,203</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1991</td>
          <td>14,091</td>
          <td>366</td>
          <td>14,457</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1992<sup>1</sup></td>
          <td>14,143</td>
          <td>373</td>
          <td>14,515</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1993</td>
          <td>14,265</td>
          <td>356</td>
          <td>14,620</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1994</td>
          <td>14,681</td>
          <td>389</td>
          <td>15,069</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1995</td>
          <td>14,021</td>
          <td>355</td>
          <td>14,376</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1996</td>
          <td>13,897</td>
          <td>324</td>
          <td>14,221</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1997</td>
          <td>15,132</td>
          <td>363</td>
          <td>15,496</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1998<sup>2</sup></td>
          <td>15,872</td>
          <td>415</td>
          <td>16,286</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>1999</td>
          <td>14,350</td>
          <td>379</td>
          <td>14,728</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2000</td>
          <td>12,369</td>
          <td>321</td>
          <td>12,691</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td>2001</td>
          <td>10,449</td>
          <td>180</td>
          <td>10,628</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td><span class="italic">Notes:</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td><sup>1</sup>53 week statistical year</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td><sup>2</sup>Figures have been rounded individually and totals will not necessarily agree with the addition of separate figures.</td>
          </tr>
          </table></p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06080'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_135'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-alan-hurst' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_135' title='Link to this speech by Mr Alan Hurst' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-alan-hurst" title="Mr Alan Hurst">Mr. Hurst</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06080">To ask the Secretary of State for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs how many pigs were on holdings in England and Wales in June of each year from 1990. [87294]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0397P0-06081'>
        <a name='S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_136'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-elliot-morley' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0397P0_20030108_CWS2_136' title='Link to this speech by Mr Elliot Morley' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
