          <p class="first-para" id="S6CV0397P0-06081">Total pigs in England are shown in the table below. Figures for Wales are a matter for the devolved authority.<table>
          <tr>
          <td>Total Pigs <span class="italic">(England)</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td><span class="italic">Number</span></td>
