          <td>6,163,443</td>
          </tr>
          </table></p><a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_238ws' title='Col. 238WS &mdash; HC Deb 08 January 2003 vol 397 c238WS' name='column_238ws' href='#column_238ws' rel='bookmark'>238WS</a><p id="S6CV0397P0-06082"><table>
          <tr>
          <td><span class="italic">Total Pigs (England)</span></td>
